        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>April. 16</date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am much obliged to you for your very courteous note &amp; kind present of your work, which I hope before long to read with all the attention which I daresay it deserves.—<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>With my best thanks | I remain | Dear Sir | yours faithfully | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
        </div>

        

        

