            <note xml:id="foot.f1">CD’s copy of Carlier’s book, <hi rend="italic">Darwinism refuted by researches in psychology</hi> (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1241.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Carlier [1872]</ref>) is in the Darwin Library–Down.</note>
